Electrical Sign Design Innovator

John Nauta began his career in the sign industry over 25 years ago. His ability to quickly master CorelDRAW and develop a deep understanding of sign fabrication and installation methods enabled him to rapidly advance from production designer to Design Director. Despite his team’s extensive experience in creating section install details, John noticed that significant time was wasted each month searching for files and modifying wall types, attachment methods, electrical provisions, and sign types. This insight led him to develop SignageDetails.com.

In 2021, John founded Signage Details, an online subscription service designed to be the ultimate resource hub for sign companies worldwide. Their exclusive, patent-pending, intuitive Select-A-Sign tool allows users to create comprehensive section details for fabricating and installing commercial signs and integrate them into their plans in as little as 60 seconds, regardless of the design program used.
